#HomesensePartner Our trip to @Homesense_US was a success! As you can tell we truly needed a refresh to make our apartment feel like the both of us and couldn’t be happier with the stand out pieces we were able to pick out. A lot of our furniture was mine from before Serena and I were together, so we wanted to change that as one of our first projects post-wedding. Our home feels comfortable, spacious and elevated thanks to our shopping trip with Homesense. It’s so nice to go into a new season as newlyweds and be able to leave all the clutter behind 🍁
#DiscoverHomesense
